quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,"“Ndipo ndithu okhala m’chigwa cha Hijr (Asamuda), Adatsutsa atumiki"
  15,81,"“Tidawapatsa zisonyezo zathu, koma sadazilabadire"
  15,82,“Iwo adali kujoba nyumba m’mapiri mwamtendere (ankaboola mapiri kuwasandutsa nyumba zawo)
  15,83,"“Choncho, chiphokoso cha chilango chidawapeza m’mawa"
  15,84,“Sichidawathandize (chuma) chomwe ankachipeza (ngakhalenso zimene ankazichita)
  15,85,"“Sitidalenge thambo ndi nthaka ndi (zonse) zapakati pake koma (kulimbikitsa) choonadi. Ndipo palibe chikaiko, Qiyâma idza. Choncho mkhululukire kukhululuka kwabwino (aliyense wokuchitira zoipa)"
  15,86,"“Ndithudi, Mbuye wako, Iye ndi Mlengi wa zonse, Wodziwa kwambiri"
  15,87,"“Ndipo ndithu takupatsa (Ayah izi) zisanu ndi ziwiri zomawerenga kawirikawiri, (Sûrat Al-Fatihah), ndi Qur’an yolemekezeka"
  15,88,"“Usatong’olere maso ako (kuyang’ana) zimene tawasangalatsa nazo mitundumitundu ya mwa iwo (monga chuma cha anthu osakhulupirira). Usawadandaulirenso iwo ndipo tsitsa phiko lako kwa okhululupirira, (uwafungatire)"
  15,89,"“Ndipo nena: “Ndithu ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera (sindikubisa chilichonse kuopera kuti chingakutsikireni chilango).”"
  15,90,“Monga momwe tidatsitsira (chilango) kwa amene adadzigawa m’magulu
  15,91,"“Omwe aichita Qur’an kukhala magawomagawo; (zina nkuzikhulupirira, zina nkuzitsutsa)"
  15,92,"“(Allah akudzilumbilira kuti:) Pali Mbuye wako, tidzawafunsa onse (tsiku la Qiyâma)"
  15,93,“Pazimene ankachita (padziko lapansi)
  15,94,"“Choncho, lengeza zimene ukulamulidwa, ndipo uwapewe opembedza mafano, (usaope chilichonse kwa iwo)"
  15,95,“Ndithu Ife tikukwanira kukuteteza ku (zoipa za) achipongwe
  15,96,"“Omwe akupanga milungu ina ndi kuiphatikiza ndi Allah, posachedwapa adziwa (zotsatira zake)"
  15,97,“Ndithu Ife tikudziwa kuti chifuwa chako chikubanika ndi zimene akunenazo
  15,98,"“(Koma pirira), lemekeza Mbuye wako pamodzi ndi kumtamanda (ndi rnbiri Zake zabwino) ndipo khala mwa olambira (Allah)"
  15,99,“Ndipo mpembedze Mbuye wako mpaka chikufike chitsimikizo (imfa)